)\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e                              \u003c/p\u003e                                                              \u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you want to refresh your memory ahead of the premiere of The Last of Us Season 2, check out the brand-new \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DSGGQXLG?tag=gamespot-preorders-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eLimited Edition Steelbook release of Season 1 on 4K Blu-ray\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e. The new edition comes with a very cool steelbook case and is on sale for $38 (was $50) at Amazon. You could display your steelbook case next to the \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/PlayStation-Figures-Accessories-Collection-Collectors/dp/B0CT8NBQF7?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eofficial action figure versions of Joel \u0026amp; Ellie\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e, who joined the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/articles/playstation-action-figure-deals-get-aloy-for-half-price-last-of-us-2-pack-for-20-off/1100-6528397/\" data-ref-id=\"1100-6528397\"\u003ePlayStation Shapes collectible lineup\u003c/a\u003e last fall. The two-pack of articulated and customizable action figures is discounted to $40 (was $50). And if you like board games, The Last of Us was recently \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Last-Us-Adventure-Cooperative-Themeborne/dp/B0DHWHG14R?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eadapted into a cooperative strategy game called Escape the Dark\u003c/a\u003e. Designed to be played solo or alongside up to four friends, the officially licensed tabletop game is available for $71.49 at Amazon.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DSGGQXLG?tag=gamespot-preorders-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last of Us Season 1 Limited Edition Steelbook (4K)\u003c/a\u003e -- $38 (\u003cdel\u003e$50\u003c/del\u003e) | Releases March 18\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DZKWSMJ2?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last of Us: Joel \u0026amp; Ellie Action Figure Pack\u003c/a\u003e -- $40 (\u003cdel\u003e$50\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Last-Us-Adventure-Cooperative-Themeborne/dp/B0DHWHG14R?tag=gamespot-promos-20\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last of Us: Escape the Dark Board Game\u003c/a\u003e -- $71.49 (\u003cdel\u003e$75\u003c/del\u003e)\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003chr/\u003e\u003ch2\u003eThe Last of Us Game Deals\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf haven\u0026#39;t played video game series yet or are looking to add physical copies to your PS5 collection, you can grab \u003ca href=\"https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?q=https%3A%2F%2Fgoto.walmart.com%2Fc%2F1804712%2F565706%2F9383%3Fveh%3Daff%26sourceid%3Dimp_000011112222333344%26u%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FThe-Last-of-Us-Part-I-PlayStation-5%2F1643604134%26subId1%3Dsubid_value\u0026amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Fthe-last-of-us-limited-edition-ps5-controller-preorders-restocked-at-major-retailers%2F1100-6529950%2F\u0026amp;event_type=click\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last of Us Part 1\u003c/a\u003e for $50 (was $70) and \u003ca href=\"https://howl.link/7o8d0t25jtgc8?article_name=Gamespot\u0026amp;article_url=https://www.gamespot.com/17422465297256?u1=subid_value\" data-target=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\"\u003eThe Last of Us Part 2 Remastered\u003c/a\u003e for $50. Meanwhile, GameSpot sister site Fanatical is offering a steep discount on The Last of Us Part 1 for PC and a 10% preorder discount for The Last of Us Par